{
  "section_id": "15-blackwell-vs-blackwell-ultra",
  "title": "Blackwell vs Blackwell Ultra",
  "title_translation": "Blackwell 与 Blackwell Ultra 对比",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "p000",
      "index": 0,
      "source": "On paper, the newly released Blackwell Ultra has the same memory bandwidth as Blackwell, the same FP8 performance and only 1.5x higher FP4 performance, but when measuring we actually see up to 1.5x better FP8 performance on the Blackwell Ultra, though we only see 1.1x better performance on FP4. This may be due to Blackwell Ultra being a newly released GPU, meaning software is not fully optimized yet.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0195",
      "parent_block_index": 195,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "On paper, the newly released Blackwell Ultra has the same memory bandwidth as Blackwell, the same FP8 performance and only 1.5x higher FP4 performance, but when measuring we actually see up to 1.5x better FP8 performance on the Blackwell Ultra, though we only see 1.1x better performance on FP4. This may be due to Blackwell Ultra being a newly released GPU, meaning software is not fully optimized yet.",
